BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p><b><i>The JUNGS are the group for 18-27-year-old men* who are into men*.</i></b></p><p></p><p>Finally\, it&#x27\;s that time again—the boys are going to the Underground!</p><p>PLEASE NOTE THE FOLLOWING INFORMATION!</p><p></p><p>The Underground is THE place to go at the MLC to live out your fetishes. Whether leather\, puppy\, uniform\, fisting\, or just naked—there&#x27\;s something for everyone here.</p><p>But it&#x27\;s also the perfect event for visitors who have had little or no experience with fetishes or are just discovering their fetish. Together with the guys from the MLC\, we will guide you through the location\, which is brightly lit just for us. This way\, you can explore everything\, touch\, try things out\, and ask lots of questions.</p><p>NOTES:</p><p></p><p>    This event is exclusively for male-identified persons aged 18 and over due to the “men only” guidelines in place at the venue.</p><p>    We will meet PUNCTUALLY at 5:30 p.m. at the Machtelfingerstraße subway station.</p><p>    It is NOT possible to arrive late!</p><p>    Depending on the time\, we may go out for something to eat afterwards. Please bring money and a valid MVV ticket with you!</p><p>    All visitors have the opportunity to go to the MLC party on the same evening. The motto is “taster party\,” so you don&#x27\;t need any special clothing to go there! Here you can find information about the dress code if you want to go to other events. If you have any questions\, please send us a message using the contact form.</p><p></p><p>Unfortunately\, this event is not barrier-free. Please come back next time or get in touch.</p><p></p><p>Translated with DeepL.com (free version)</p>\n\n(Error: The event had no end date)
DURATION:PT2H57M
DTSTART:20250808T153000Z
SUMMARY:JUNGS meet MLC Underground
UID:8bf4edaa-3262-4afc-897b-777d853402f0@8bf4.org
END:VEVENT
