DESCRIPTION:<p></p><p>Unfortunately\, we have to cancel the event since we dont have enough organising people.</p><p><b>But if you want to\, you can come visit the diversity cafe\, Blumenstr 29\, that&#x27\;s open from 4 to 8pm! You can get coffee and cake for a good price there and it&#x27\;s definitely worth a visit!</b></p><p>We hope you have a good time and we&#x27\;ll see you on the 15th</p><p>Best wishes\, your Wilma Team. </p><p>If you ever want to help or maybe even organize and event\, write us via our contact form! We&#x27\;re happy about every helping hand!</p>
