BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p>Every 1. Sunday a month\, we are playing video games in the diversity Café. Come over with your friends or alone and have fun playing mario kart\, switch sports or just dance. Enjoy our cakes\, sandwiches and drinks. Of course\, you can come over for talking with friends or read a book as well.</p><p>Our relaxed café afternoon for everyone up to 27 years old. You can meet your friends in a quiet atmosphere or get to know other LGBTIAQ* youth in the afternoon or over the weekend.</p><p>Our diverse team hosts our youth café and treats you to all kinds of cold and hot drinks as well as hearty and sweet food at our usual low prices.</p><h4>Our <a id="7" linktype="page">diversity Café</a> opens regularly:</h4><ul><li>every Tuesday from 4 pm. to 8 pm.</li><li>every Thursday from 4 pm to 8 pm and</li><li>every Sunday from 3 pm to 7 pm</li></ul><p>You can also find up-to-date information on social media (e.g. in the event of short-term closures).</p><h4>Contact us!</h4><p>If you’d like to get in touch with our diversity Café directly – for example\, if you’d like to volunteer or organise a small event with us at the diversity Café (such as a reading\, concert or poetry slam) – then contact us <a id="2097" linktype="page"><b>using the contact form</b></a> or talk to us at during opening hours.</p><p><b>We are happy about active support and show you as a beginner everything in a relaxed way.</b></p>
DTEND:20250803T170000Z
