DESCRIPTION:<p><i>Invited is everyone 27 years or under who doesn‘t belong to the binary gender system or is questioning. If you have any questions or doubts\, please feel free to contact us! We&#x27\;re looking forward to seeing you.</i></p><p></p><p><b>More info coming soon :)</b></p><p></p><p><i>Our youth centre is unfortunately not accessible. Should you rely on an accessible entry\, please write</i> <a href="https://diversity-muenchen.de/en/gruppen/enbees/contact/"><i>us here</i></a><i>. We might be able to find a short-term solution.</i></p>\n\n(Error: The event had no end date)
